author: COMSOL
description:
In this tutorial, you will use the Offset Faces and Transform Faces operations as a way to reparameterize existing holes in a bracket geometry imported from a STEP file. The mass of the bracket is minimized with limits for both the lowest natural frequency, and for the maximum stress in a static load case.

Geometrical constraints, formulated as parameter expressions, are enforced during the optimization to maintain the design intent of the geometry.
